      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's weird because we checked the scrap logs and the breakage reports and they don't show this kind of volume. it's like the items are just... gone. no damage, no waste, just missing from the bins. is there anything else that could cause items to just disappear without leaving a paper trail or a physical sign? something that's just hard to track?",
